detail.name: Babidi
detail.effect:
[On Play] If your Leader has 《Majin》 in its special traits, play up to 1 Battle Card with a cost of 3 or less and 《Majin》 in its special traits from your hand.
[When KO'd] If your opponent has 6 or more cards in their hand, your opponent discards 1 card from their hand.

detail.name: バビディ
detail.effect: 【登場時】自分のリーダーが特徴《魔人》を持つ場合、自分の手札のコスト3以下の特徴《魔人》を持つバトルカード1枚までを登場させる。【KO時】相手の手札が6枚以上の場合、相手は自身の手札1枚を捨てる。

faq.question: When your opponent has 6 cards in their hand, they use FB04-093 <Majin Buu : Evil>'s [Activate Main] skill to KO this card, and now they have 5 cards in their hand. Can you then use this card's [When KO'd] skill to make your opponent discard 1 card from their hand?

Your opponent used FS01-16 <God Kamehameha> when they had 6 cards in their hand, then this card was KO'd when they had 5 cards in their hand. Can you use this card's [When KO'd] skill to make your opponent discard 1 card from their hand?
相手の手札が6枚の時に、FB04-093「魔人ブウ：悪」の【起動 メイン】スキルでこのカードをKOをし、相手の手札が5枚になりました。その後、このカードの【KO時】スキルで手札を捨てさせることはできますか？
相手の手札が6枚の時に相手がFS01-16「ゴッドかめはめ波」を使用し、相手の手札が5枚の状態でこのカードがKOされました。このカードの【KO時】スキルで相手の手札を捨てさせることはできますか？
